      <title>数学课总结</title>
      <link href="/2024/04/19/%E6%95%B0%E5%AD%A6%E8%AF%BE%E6%80%BB%E7%BB%93/"/>
      <url>/2024/04/19/%E6%95%B0%E5%AD%A6%E8%AF%BE%E6%80%BB%E7%BB%93/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<link rel="stylesheet" class="aplayer-secondary-style-marker" href="\assets\css\APlayer.min.css"><script src="\assets\js\APlayer.min.js" class="aplayer-secondary-script-marker"></script><script class="meting-secondary-script-marker" src="\assets\js\Meting.min.js"></script><p>对于一个优化问题，<br>$min\qquad f_0x\<br>s.t.\qquad Ax\leq b…\<br>\qquad Gx &#x3D;c…$</p><p>构造拉格朗日函数：<br>$L(x,\lambda,v) &#x3D; f_0x + \sum\lambda_i(A_ix-b_i) + \sum v (G_ix-c)$<br>注意这个式子既可以写成向量的形式（消去下标 i），也要保证拉格朗日函数的值和$f_0x$保持一致，一般是标量，所以$\lambda 和v$要适时改成转置形式</p><p>然后求拉格朗日函数的梯度，得到最小值 $min L(x,\lambda,v)$，因为对偶函数$g(x) &#x3D; inf L(x,\lambda,v)$，即对偶函数可以通过求拉格朗日函数的最小值得到</p><p> 求解要点：目标函数必须是最小化（可以通过取负来转换）；不等式约束必须是 **&lt;<em><em>（可以换方向）<br>① KKT 条件，就是凸优化问题能通过对偶函数取得全局最优解的 3 个条件，有时可以通过 KKT 直接得到最优解（这是一组方程组）<br>② 对偶问题求最优解，凸优化问题的强对偶性成立，所以可以通过将对偶问题的 max 的 解$\lambda^</em>、v^*$代回拉格朗日函数来求 $x^</em>$<br><img src="https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2024/png/36029610/1704871882259-53722aa0-fc63-42b8-a261-fc3946244eb5.png#averageHue=%23f4f4f4&clientId=u5edb0eee-1f0d-4&from=paste&height=231&id=u028945b4&originHeight=529&originWidth=1314&originalType=binary&ratio=1&rotation=0&showTitle=false&size=194637&status=done&style=none&taskId=ufce97631-7db3-42fe-a854-4d82b4134d9&title=&width=573" alt="image.png"></p><p>矩阵范数：<br>$l_1$范数<img src="https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2024/png/36029610/1704887899569-8281dd18-7a62-4b60-b567-2bd2c52c0fa8.png#averageHue=%23c6c6c9&clientId=u23f82b39-6e26-4&from=paste&height=56&id=uc75ef587&originHeight=83&originWidth=288&originalType=binary&ratio=1&rotation=0&showTitle=false&size=18096&status=done&style=none&taskId=uf1a7cfeb-e823-4b7f-9347-6e7a8fbc2c4&title=&width=193" alt="image.png"><br>$l_\infty$范数<img src="https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2024/png/36029610/1704887970496-de9996f9-1cf7-40fa-b696-bf57f5c38fac.png#averageHue=%23c0bfc2&clientId=u23f82b39-6e26-4&from=paste&height=62&id=u971b31d2&originHeight=125&originWidth=517&originalType=binary&ratio=1&rotation=0&showTitle=false&size=25724&status=done&style=none&taskId=u67e4ec10-561a-4aec-a094-6f5fde1c39d&title=&width=257" alt="image.png"></p><p>$Frobenius$范数，F 范数、$l_2$范数：<img src="https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2024/png/36029610/1704888010666-18725030-6b41-4e9f-969d-e1a6a497db99.png#averageHue=%23adacb0&clientId=u23f82b39-6e26-4&from=paste&height=68&id=ube5ea1e7&originHeight=134&originWidth=751&originalType=binary&ratio=1&rotation=0&showTitle=false&size=42916&status=done&style=none&taskId=ue61ef56b-342a-40bc-b0b2-410857f6323&title=&width=383" alt="image.png"></p><p>$l_p$范数诱导出的算子范数：<img src="https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2024/png/36029610/1704888947105-175d3017-39d3-4ce6-a1b8-980cf3ea73ad.png#averageHue=%239da2a4&clientId=u48fe942a-41c4-4&from=paste&height=41&id=u296baa3a&originHeight=114&originWidth=380&originalType=binary&ratio=1&rotation=0&showTitle=false&size=25071&status=done&style=none&taskId=u788f7b4b-6d54-450c-aac1-344169ef890&title=&width=135" alt="image.png"><br><img src="https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2024/png/36029610/1704888933579-087d8f61-0883-4b72-829c-d4ddcaeb92d2.png#averageHue=%239d9ea1&clientId=u48fe942a-41c4-4&from=paste&height=304&id=u1ae2f80b&originHeight=344&originWidth=436&originalType=binary&ratio=1&rotation=0&showTitle=true&size=68473&status=done&style=none&taskId=ub2b6b5f7-c5cb-441a-9260-b12a92b93ae&title=%E6%9C%80%E5%A4%A7%E5%88%97%E5%92%8C%E3%80%81%E6%9C%80%E5%A4%A7%E8%A1%8C%E5%92%8C%E3%80%81%E6%9C%80%E5%A4%A7%E8%B0%B1%EF%BC%88%E7%89%B9%E5%BE%81%E5%80%BC%EF%BC%89&width=385" alt="最大列和、最大行和、最大谱（特征值）" title="最大列和、最大行和、最大谱（特征值）"></p><p>$df &#x3D; Tr((\frac{\partial f}{\partial A})^TdA)$</p><p>关于逆矩阵的微分<br><img src="https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2024/png/36029610/1704936943636-68d94714-a211-4e52-af5f-c83a223f30ff.png#averageHue=%23eae7ea&clientId=ud2e2b1af-4512-4&from=paste&height=162&id=ufd2d5864&originHeight=289&originWidth=832&originalType=binary&ratio=1&rotation=0&showTitle=false&size=138857&status=done&style=none&taskId=u25268bf8-9586-4973-8c4e-c56fb66ff0e&title=&width=467" alt="image.png"></p>]]></content>
      
      
      
